        "content": "### Read Pending Queue (MySQL)\n\nmySql — `select` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Keep Valid Payloads · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 MySQL connection",
